    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated chicken</strong> and cook for 8-9 min on each side or until golden brown, crispy and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> crispy chicken</strong></p><p>Once the chicken is cooked, remove from the pan and set aside, reserve the pan</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 5,
