    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>brioche</strong> <strong>halves</strong> to a baking tray, cut side up, and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once the chips and pepper are cooked, remove <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and set aside for serving</p><p>Mix the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>through the chips with the<strong> spring onion strips</strong> and season with a generous grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>– these are your <strong>salt & pepper chips</strong></p>",
