    {
      "instruction": "<p>Carefully wipe the reserved pan with some kitchen paper (it will be hot!) and return it to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sweet & sour sauce</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened</p><p>Once thickened, add the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> and give everything a good mix up until the chicken is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>sweet & sour chicken</strong></p>",
